data.description: Elegant 3-Bedroom Retreat with Modern Updates and Outdoor Paradise in Chatsworth Cul-de-Sac. Discover the epitome of California living in this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.25-bathroom residence, offering 2,101 square feet of comfortable living space. Situated on a spacious 5,167 square foot lot in a peaceful Chatsworth cul-de-sac, this meticulously maintained home is a true gem.This residence has been updated with newer windows, HVAC system, water heater, and flooring, ensuring a contemporary and energy-efficient living environment. Spacious Primary Suite, retreat to the expansive primary bedroom featuring a full bathroom and small walk in closet, creating a private sanctuary within your own home. Entertainment Delight, two inviting living rooms, one with a built-in bar, offer versatile spaces for gatherings and relaxation. The huge kitchen presents tremendous potential for culinary enthusiasts. With abundant space, it's a canvas waiting for your personal touch. Enjoy meals in both the formal dining room and the cozy breakfast nook, providing options for intimate dinners or larger gatherings. One of the bedrooms boasts a huge private balcony, offering a perfect spot to enjoy your morning coffee or unwind in the evening while taking in the scenic surroundings. Relax in the above-ground spa under the gazebo cover, creating a tranquil retreat within your own property. The home includes a 2-car garage with a convenient laundry area, adding practicality to your daily routine. Step out to a beautifully manicured front and backyard, complete with hardscape and artificial turf for easy maintenance. Revel in the serenity of a private oasis, surrounded by towering privacy trees. This Chatsworth residence is a rare find, showcasing a perfect blend of modern comforts, stylish updates, and an outdoor haven.
